            <li>Support for temperature, humidity, motion, and light sensors</li>
            <li>Control of lights, thermostats, and smart plugs</li>
            <li>Customizable automation rules with conditional logic</li>
            <li>Energy usage monitoring and optimization</li>
            <li>Mobile app for remote control (iOS and Android)</li>
